        </h1>
        <p className="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl opacity-90 animate-fade-in delay-200">
          Track, Train, and Transform â€“ Your fitness journey starts here!
        </p>

        <button className="mt-6 px-6 py-3 bg-yellow-400 text-black font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:bg-yellow-500 transition duration-300 animate-fade-in delay-400">
